query:
SELECT p.id, p.userId, p.firstName, p.lastName, p.email, p.courseId, u.id as actualUserId, u.email as userEmail
FROM participants p 
LEFT JOIN users u ON p.userId = u.id 
WHERE p.email = 's.sachs@sachs-media.com'
ORDER BY p.id DESC
LIMIT 5;
